*   Detailed travel insurance options with costs, suitable for their international lifestyle.
*   Any recommended additional services or enhancements with costs.
*   A clear breakdown of how these proposals offer better protection and cost efficiency compared to the current situation.
*   A complete monthly/annual cost breakdown for all proposed items.

We look forward to reviewing your suggestions.

